name: Rusko, Clockmaker
oracle_text:
When Rusko, Clockmaker enters the battlefield, conjure a card named Midnight Clock onto the battlefield.
Whenever you cast a noncreature spell, put an hour counter on each permanent you control named Midnight Clock. Each opponent loses 1 life and you gain 1 life.

name: Legion of Clay
oracle_text:
Creatures you control have trample.
Whenever one or more nontoken artifacts enter under your control, creatures you control perpetually get +1/+1.

name: Patchplate Resolute
oracle_text:

Unearth {1}{W}

name: Raddic, Tal Zealot
oracle_text:
Hexproof from white and from black

name: Tawnos Endures
oracle_text: Exile target creature. It gains "At the beginning of your upkeep, if this card is exiled, it perpetually gets +1/+1, then you may put it onto the battlefield."

name: Crucias, Titan of the Waves
oracle_text: At the beginning of your end step, you may discard a card. If you do, create a Treasure token and choose ambitious or expedient. If you chose ambitious, seek a card with greater mana value than the discarded card. If you chose expedient, seek a card with lesser mana value than the discarded card.

name: Hurkyl's Prodigy
oracle_text:
When Hurkyl's Prodigy enters, create a tapped Powerstone token.
Whenever Hurkyl's Prodigy attacks, you may pay {2}. If you do, Hurkyl's Prodigy can't be blocked this turn and it perpetually gets +2/+0.

oracle_text:

oracle_text: Put two +1/+1 counters on each of X target lands you control. They each become 0/0 Elemental creatures with reach, haste, and "When this creature leaves the battlefield, conjure a card named Forest onto the battlefield tapped." They're still lands.

name: Argivian Welcome
oracle_text:
Destroy up to one target creature with power 4 or greater.

name: Penregon Besieged
oracle_text:

name: Perilous Iteration
oracle_text: Seek a card with mana value 2 or less and a card with mana value 3 or greater. Discard those cards at the beginning of your next turn's end step.

name: Melt Through
oracle_text: Melt Through deals 2 damage to any target. If it's a creature, it perpetually gains "As long as this creature is on the battlefield, damage isn't removed from it during cleanup steps."

name: Gixian Recycler
oracle_text:

Unearth {1}{B}

name: Fallaji Antiquarian
oracle_text:
Haste

oracle_text:

• Up to one target Soldier perpetually gets +1/+1 and gains flying.

oracle_text:
Starting intensity 1

oracle_text:
Flying

name: Assemble the Team
oracle_text: Search the top third of your library, rounded up, for a card. Put that card into your hand, then shuffle.

name: Kayla's Kindling
oracle_text:
When Kayla's Kindling enters, it deals 2 damage to any target.
At the beginning of your upkeep, draft a card from Kayla's Kindling's spellbook and exile it. Until end of turn, you may cast that card.

oracle_text:
Flying, haste
When Tomakul Phoenix dies, it perpetually gets +2/+2.
At the beginning of combat on your turn, you may pay {X}{R}, where X is Tomakul Phoenix's power. If you do, return it from your graveyard to the battlefield.

name: Great Desert Hellion
oracle_text:
Starting intensity 1
Menace

oracle_text:

name: Norn's Disassembly
